{"tid":253048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小心電騙】 誘到酒店Login銀行戶口 工程師被騙150萬人仔","createTime":"2017-05-22T05:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T05:25:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03b916899054823c6774452f666f2400c7ba7c6a","tid":253048,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"【12:43更新】男事主為來港工作的工程師<br />\n<br />\n一名38歲姓陳男事主，上月4日在葵涌區辦公室內，接獲一名操廣東話的不明男子來電，對方自稱入境處職員，並指他涉嫌與一宗洗黑錢案件有關，電話其後轉駁至一名自稱上海公安的男子，並要求他到一個僻靜地方作調查。<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，男事主早年由內地來港工作，現已獲得香港身份證，在港任職工程師。</span><br />\n<br />\n男事主根據指示，來到皇崗一酒店，按指示將三個內地銀行的記憶棒、插入酒店電腦並登入戶口，再登入一個內地通訊網頁，以供對方以遠端方式作調查之用。<br />\n<br />\n兩日後男事主發現三個戶口內共150萬元人民幣不見了，懷疑受騙，遂於昨日到旺角警署報案。經初步調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，將交由葵青警區刑事部跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56724930&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56724930%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170522&d=z1Z9%2FhyuGVbDXJZ%2FGqhOodZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=77660434\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56724930%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170522&h=b379d2e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56724930&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170522</a>"},{"pid":"d80793480372cdd3e70312ddfe1dfe13fb4a0e14","tid":253048,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:24:56.000Z","msg":"係支國果陣做左好多衰野<br />\n<br />\n比人一嚇就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b7ec4f3a190bc19d00ba1daf92832d82f55e44","tid":253048,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:25:32.000Z","msg":"我開始懷疑透過電騙使黑錢<br />\n再蠢都唔會咁中招...."}]}